HTTP POST /api/users/register

curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/users/register   -H "Content-Type: application/json"   -d '{
    "username": "mark",
    "email": "mark@example.com",
    "password": "StrongPassword123",
    "password2": "StrongPassword123",
    "signing_public_key": "BASE64_PUBLIC_KEY"
  }'


{"signing_public_key":["Encodage de clé publique invalide (base64)."]}

OK 